    "innerText": "1. Tiṇakaṭṭhasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "124"
      },
      ". Upasaggo ",
      " samāsavisaye sasādhanaṃ kiriyaṃ dassetīti vuttaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘ñāṇena anugantvāpī’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vassasataṃ vassasahassa"
      },
      "nti nidassanamattametaṃ, tato bhiyyopi anugantvā anamataggo eva saṃsāro. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Agga"
      },
      "-saddo idha mariyādavacano, anuddesikañcetaṃ vacananti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘aparicchinnapubbāparakoṭiko’’"
      },
      "ti. Aññathā antimabhavikaparicchinnakatavimuttiparipācanīyadhammādīnaṃ vasena aparicchinnapubbāparakoṭi na sakkā vattuṃ. Saṃsaraṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "saṃsāro. Pacchimāpi na paññāyati"
      },
      " andhabālānaṃ vasenāti adhippāyo. Tenāha bhagavā ‘‘dīgho bālāna saṃsāro’’ti (dha. pa. 60). ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vemajjheyeva pana sattā saṃsaranti"
      },
      " pubbāparakoṭīnaṃ alabbhanīyattā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Attho paritto hoti"
      },
      " yathābhūtāvabodhābhāvato. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Buddhasamaye"
      },
      "ti sāsaneti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Attho mahā"
      },
      " yathābhūtāvabodhisambhavato, atthassa vipulatāya taṃsadisā upamā natthīti parittaṃyeva upamaṃ āharantīti adhippāyo. Idāni vuttamevatthaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘pāḷiyaṃ hī’’"
      },
      "tiādinā samattheti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mātu mātaro"
      },
      "ti mātu mātāmahiyo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tassevā"
      },
      "ti dukkhasseva. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tibba"
      },
      "nti dukkhapariyāyoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "124. Upasaggo samāsavisaye sasādhanaṃ kiriyaṃ dassetīti vuttaṃ ‘‘ñāṇena anugantvāpī’’ti. Vassasataṃ vassasahassanti nidassanamattametaṃ, tato bhiyyopi anugantvā anamataggo eva saṃsāro. Agga-saddo idha mariyādavacano, anuddesikañcetaṃ vacananti āha ‘‘aparicchinnapubbāparakoṭiko’’ti. Aññathā antimabhavikaparicchinnakatavimuttiparipācanīyadhammādīnaṃ vasena aparicchinnapubbāparakoṭi na sakkā vattuṃ. Saṃsaraṇaṃ saṃsāro. Pacchimāpi na paññāyati andhabālānaṃ vasenāti adhippāyo. Tenāha bhagavā ‘‘dīgho bālāna saṃsāro’’ti (dha. pa. 60). Vemajjheyeva pana sattā saṃsaranti pubbāparakoṭīnaṃ alabbhanīyattā. Attho paritto hoti yathābhūtāvabodhābhāvato. Buddhasamayeti sāsaneti attho. Attho mahā yathābhūtāvabodhisambhavato, atthassa vipulatāya taṃsadisā upamā natthīti parittaṃyeva upamaṃ āharantīti adhippāyo. Idāni vuttamevatthaṃ ‘‘pāḷiyaṃ hī’’tiādinā samattheti. Mātu mātaroti mātu mātāmahiyo. Tassevāti dukkhasseva. Tibbanti dukkhapariyāyoti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Tiṇakaṭṭhasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
