    },
    "innerText": "2. Pathavīsuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "125"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mahāpathavi"
      },
      "nti avisesena anavasesapariyādāyinīti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘cakkavāḷapariyanta’’"
      },
      "nti. Parikappavacanañcetaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "125.Mahāpathavinti avisesena anavasesapariyādāyinīti āha ‘‘cakkavāḷapariyanta’’nti. Parikappavacanañcetaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Pathavīsuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "3. Assusuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "126"
      },
      ". Kandanaṃ ",
      " sasaddaṃ, rodanaṃ pana kevalamevāti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘kandantānanti sasaddaṃ rudamānāna’’"
      },
      "nti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pavatta"
      },
      "nti sandanavasena pavattaṃ. ‘‘Sinerurasmīhi paricchinnesū’’ti saṅkhepena vuttamatthaṃ vivaranto ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘sinerussā’’"
      },
      "tiādimāha. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Maṇimaya"
      },
      "nti indanīlamaṇimayaṃ. Sinerussa pubbadakkhiṇakoṇasamapadesā ‘‘pubbadakkhiṇapassā’’ti adhippetā. Tehi nikkhantarajatarasmiyo indanīlarasmiyo ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ekato hutvā. Tāsaṃ rasmīnaṃ antaresū"
      },
      "ti tāsaṃ catūhi koṇehi nikkhantarasmīnaṃ catūsu antaresu. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cattāro"
      },
      "ti dakkhiṇādibhedā cattāro mahāsamuddā honti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Viasana"
      },
      "nti visesena khepanaṃ. Kiṃ pana tanti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘vināsoti attho’’"
      },
      "ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "126. Kandanaṃ sasaddaṃ, rodanaṃ pana kevalamevāti āha ‘‘kandantānanti sasaddaṃ rudamānāna’’nti. Pavattanti sandanavasena pavattaṃ. ‘‘Sinerurasmīhi paricchinnesū’’ti saṅkhepena vuttamatthaṃ vivaranto ‘‘sinerussā’’tiādimāha. Maṇimayanti indanīlamaṇimayaṃ. Sinerussa pubbadakkhiṇakoṇasamapadesā ‘‘pubbadakkhiṇapassā’’ti adhippetā. Tehi nikkhantarajatarasmiyo indanīlarasmiyo ca ekato hutvā. Tāsaṃ rasmīnaṃ antaresūti tāsaṃ catūhi koṇehi nikkhantarasmīnaṃ catūsu antaresu. Cattāroti dakkhiṇādibhedā cattāro mahāsamuddā honti. Viasananti visesena khepanaṃ. Kiṃ pana tanti āha ‘‘vināsoti attho’’ti."
  },
