    "innerText": "5. Pabbatasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "128"
      },
      ". ‘‘Anamataggassa saṃsārassa dīghatamattā na sukaraṃ nasukara’’nti aṭṭhakathāpāṭho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kathaṃ nacchindatī"
      },
      "ti kathaṃ na pariyosāpeti, kāyacipi gahaṇatāyāti adhippāyo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tayo kappāsaṃsū"
      },
      "ti tayo ekakappāsaṃsū. Yehi naṃ phuṭṭhaṃ, tatopi sukhumataraṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sāsapamattaṃ"
      },
      " khīyeyya pabbataṃ sabbabhāgehi aticiravelaṃ parimajjante."
    ],
    "innerText": "128. ‘‘Anamataggassa saṃsārassa dīghatamattā na sukaraṃ nasukara’’nti aṭṭhakathāpāṭho. Kathaṃ nacchindatīti kathaṃ na pariyosāpeti, kāyacipi gahaṇatāyāti adhippāyo. Tayo kappāsaṃsūti tayo ekakappāsaṃsū. Yehi naṃ phuṭṭhaṃ, tatopi sukhumataraṃ sāsapamattaṃ khīyeyya pabbataṃ sabbabhāgehi aticiravelaṃ parimajjante."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Pabbatasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Sāsapasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "129"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Nagara"
      },
      "nti ",
      " nagarasaṅkhepena pākārena parikkhittataṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. Anto pana sabbaso vicittasāsapehi eva puṇṇaṃ, evaṃ cuṇṇikābaddhaṃ. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘na pana…pe… daṭṭhabba’’"
      },
      "nti."
    ],
    "innerText": "129.Nagaranti nagarasaṅkhepena pākārena parikkhittataṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. Anto pana sabbaso vicittasāsapehi eva puṇṇaṃ, evaṃ cuṇṇikābaddhaṃ. Tenāha ‘‘na pana…pe… daṭṭhabba’’nti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Sāsapasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
