    "innerText": "9. Daṇḍasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "132"
      },
      ". Navame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "khitto"
      },
      "ti punappunaṃ khitto. Ekavārañhi khitto mūlādīsu ekeneva nipateyya. Tathā sati adhippeto pātassa aniyamo na nidassito siyā. Tattha ca dhammaṃ suṇantā bhikkhū manussaloke, te sandhāya ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘asmā lokā’’"
      },
      "ti āha, tadaññaṃ sandhāya ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘paraloka’’"
      },
      "nti. Tassa tassa vā puggalassa yathādhippeto ayaṃ loko, tadañño paraloko."
    ],
    "innerText": "132. Navame khittoti punappunaṃ khitto. Ekavārañhi khitto mūlādīsu ekeneva nipateyya. Tathā sati adhippeto pātassa aniyamo na nidassito siyā. Tattha ca dhammaṃ suṇantā bhikkhū manussaloke, te sandhāya ‘‘asmā lokā’’ti āha, tadaññaṃ sandhāya ‘‘paraloka’’nti. Tassa tassa vā puggalassa yathādhippeto ayaṃ loko, tadañño paraloko."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Daṇḍasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
