        },
        "innerText": "Ekaṃ apadānaṃ āharitvā dasseti"
      },
      " ‘‘evaṃ saṃvegaṃ janetvā bhikkhū visesaṃ pāpessāmī’’ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Catūhena ārohanti"
      },
      " catuyojanubbedhattā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dvinnaṃ buddhāna"
      },
      "nti kakusandhassa koṇāgamanassa cāti imesaṃ dvinnaṃ buddhānaṃ. ‘‘Tivarā rohitassā suppiyā’’ti manussānaṃ tasmiṃ tasmiṃ kāle samaññā tattha desanāmavasena jātāti veditabbā, yathā etarahi māgadhāti."
    ],
    "innerText": "143.Ekaṃ apadānaṃ āharitvā dasseti ‘‘evaṃ saṃvegaṃ janetvā bhikkhū visesaṃ pāpessāmī’’ti. Catūhena ārohanti catuyojanubbedhattā. Dvinnaṃ buddhānanti kakusandhassa koṇāgamanassa cāti imesaṃ dvinnaṃ buddhānaṃ. ‘‘Tivarā rohitassā suppiyā’’ti manussānaṃ tasmiṃ tasmiṃ kāle samaññā tattha desanāmavasena jātāti veditabbā, yathā etarahi māgadhāti."
  },
  {
