        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vaḍḍhitvā"
      },
      "ti dasavassāyukabhāvato paṭṭhāya yāva asaṅkhyeyyāyukabhāvā vaḍḍhitvā. ‘‘Parihīna’’nti vatvā taṃ parihīnabhāvaṃ dassento ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘katha’’"
      },
      "ntiādimāha. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yaṃ āyuppamāṇesū"
      },
      "ti yattakaṃ āyuppamāṇesūti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Puna vassasatanti paṭhamavassasatato uparivassasataṃ jīvanako nāma manusso natthi. Parihīnasadisaṃ kataṃ desanāya. Vaḍḍhitvāti dasavassāyukabhāvato paṭṭhāya yāva asaṅkhyeyyāyukabhāvā vaḍḍhitvā. ‘‘Parihīna’’nti vatvā taṃ parihīnabhāvaṃ dassento ‘‘katha’’ntiādimāha. Yaṃ āyuppamāṇesūti yattakaṃ āyuppamāṇesūti."
  },
